50.1.hd_quote: Humbleness of origin that benefits rather than restricts destiny.
50.1.behavioral_axis: Starts from humble position and refines values that actually work for the tribe.
50.1.shadow_axis: Embarrassment about origins; over-refinement to prove worth.

50.2.hd_quote: The strength of purpose that can enjoy overcoming adversity to achieve its goals.
50.2.behavioral_axis: Keeps the tribe’s values intact even when opposed or conditioned.
50.2.shadow_axis: Withdraws when opposed; values get bent to avoid conflict.

50.3.hd_quote: The Moon exalted, that when unable to make it alone will naturally align itself with nurturing and protective forces.
50.3.behavioral_axis: Knows values are upheld better with support and bonding.
50.3.shadow_axis: Resents having to curry favor for survival.

50.4.behavioral_axis: Can hold strength even when surrounded by inferior values.
50.4.shadow_axis: Turns inferior values into success; may spread corruption.

50.5.hd_quote: When continuity has brought success, it should not be tampered with.
50.5.behavioral_axis: Guards proven rules of caring; keeps the cauldron stable.
50.5.shadow_axis: Rebels against the very methods that made things work.

50.6.hd_quote: The gift in a position of power to maintain harmony even in severity.
50.6.behavioral_axis: Uses power to keep values alive without losing relationship field.
50.6.shadow_axis: Maintains values but alienates people through moodiness.
